      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, reliable choice for someone needing a daily driver without the high cost of a newer model. The engine is steady and the transmission shifts as it should, though you may notice some minor interior wear and typical exterior blemishes consistent with its age. It has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure it remains dependable for your commutes, even if it lacks some of the modern refinements. Expect a functional, honest car that gets the job done reliably.",
